Holy shit. You are an asshole.

20:39.567 --> 20:40.800
Florence!

20:40.825 --> 20:41.516
Emma?

20:41.541 --> 20:43.805
Good news... I was
right. It was Mengshu.

20:43.830 --> 20:45.496
What? Isn't that awesome?

20:45.521 --> 20:49.129
- Oh, my God.
- Yeah, also, Yolonzo's dead.

20:49.154 --> 20:50.296
- Oh.
- [Coughing]

20:50.320 --> 20:52.903
- Oh, my God!
- [Gagging]

